    \mu_3 = \frac{2}{3} \mathbb{E}\left( \min \left( \frac{U_1 U_2}{1 - U_1 U_2}, \frac{1- U_1 U_2}{U_1 U_2} \right) \right) = \frac{1}{18} \left( \pi^2 + 12 (\log^2(2) - 1) \right)  \approx 0.201947 
